{"tid":2046921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"零零後太黄：01-02年可新增選民40000人，登記只有9000人","createTime":"2020-06-01T17:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T23:43:26.000Z","uid":7439,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0297176ca038a91256873f6837f05998227eacea","tid":2046921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"2019年正式選民登記冊 25/9/2019 發表<br />\n2020年正式選民登記冊 25/7/2020 發表<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">換言之25/9/2019-25/7/2020出世嘅今年先可以正式登記成為選民</span><br />\n<br />\n出生嬰兒數目<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71812FA2018XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB71812FA2018XXXXB0100.pdf&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns81pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=35abf235\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71812FA2018XXXXB0100.pdf</a><br />\n2001年 48219<br />\n2002年 48209<br />\n<br />\n由於唔知出生日期具體分佈<br />\n只可直接➗平均數<br />\n2001 48219✖️97/365=12814<br />\n2002 48209✖️206/365=27208<br />\n=40022<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">估算呢批新一年先可以成為新選民人數有至少4萬</span><br />\n(*2020DSE學校考生=45931)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/2018PR_sex%20and%20age_LC_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2018PR_sex%2520and%2520age_LC_c.pdf&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns81pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=2a563970\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/2018PR_sex%20and%20age_LC_c.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/2019PR_sex%20and%20age_LC_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019PR_sex%2520and%2520age_LC_c.pdf&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns81pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=a414884e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/2019PR_sex%20and%20age_LC_c.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/2020PR_sex%20and%20age_LC_c.pdf\" data-s