.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020PR_sex%2520and%2520age_LC_c.pdf&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns81pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=1a254269\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/2020PR_sex%20and%20age_LC_c.pdf</a><br />\n2018年正式登記冊<br />\n18-20 98506<br />\n2019年正式登記冊<br />\n18-20 <span style=\"color: red;\">110611</span><br />\n2020年臨時登記冊<br />\n18-20 <span style=\"color: red;\">119785</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2020年臨時登記冊，18-20歳新增得九千個選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n注意，係18-20歳，計埋00 01漏網之漁(約四萬九)<br />\n<ins>呢八、九萬人，新增得九千個選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T18:19:17.000Z","msg":"選委會 統計處啲數唔撚夾的<br />\n連人口分佈都唔撚並排的<br />\n所以都只係估算 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">錯就肯定唔少</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好唔記得成人唔一定就係選民</span><br />\n投票率係比照選民人數而非成人人數<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成人本身嘅登記率、以全港成人計算嘅投票率反而變咗一個迷</span><br />\n<br />\n但人口普查又多以15-24、15-19等計算，最簡單嘅18以上以下反而唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">所以只係睇數估，全港成人登記選民比率應該係高過65% 估架咋</span><br />\n<br />\n18-25登記人數38萬，68%，唔高得平均幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n好多野荒廢丟空發臭wfc多年<br />\n2019先如獲至寶，衰太遲係無得怪人的<br />\n<br />\n咁遲起步，妄想一步登天係更無可能的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2344527eff453202c7b217dcb9c177f84c31be5","tid":2046921,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:43:26.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">2020年臨時登記冊，18-20歳新增得九千個選民[sosad]#good#\n注意，係18-20歳，計埋00 01漏網之漁(約四萬九)\n呢八、九萬人，新增得九千個選民:)</code></pre><br />\n<a 